      <akn:section eId="sec_44_108_03">
        <akn:num>44-108.03</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Functional assessment.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-108_03_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Level of functioning in activities of daily living including bathing, dressing, grooming, eating, toileting, and mobility;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-108_03_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Level of support and intervention, including any special equipment and  supplies, required to compensate for the individualâ€™s deficits in activities  of daily living;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-108_03_3">
      <akn:num>(3)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Current physical or psychological symptoms of the individual requiring  monitoring, support, or other intervention by the ALR;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-108_03_4">
      <akn:num>(4)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Capacity of the individual for making personal and healthcare related decisions;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-108_03_5">
      <akn:num>(5)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Presence of disruptive behavior or behavior which presents a risk to the  physical or emotional health and safety of self or others;</akn:p></akn:content>
